The Keiser Report  No. 230
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Saturday, 31 December 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy present a New Year's special featuring outrageous predictions, bloopers and Berlusconi's 2012 Bunga Bunga Guide to finance. They look back to some 2010 predictions that came true in 2011 and look at the future of European bank runs, rising US treasury yields and the Jim Rogers - Marc Faber Chinese showdown.

 that counters the monotone of mainstream corporate media.
